<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>No Rockfall â€” Dashboard</title>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
      tailwind.config = {
        theme: {
          extend: {
            fontFamily: {
              display: ["Inter", "ui-sans-serif", "system-ui"],
            },
          },
        },
      };
    </script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-100 font-display text-slate-800">
    <nav class="bg-white shadow-sm border-b border-slate-200">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div
            class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-600 text-white font-bold"
          >
            NR
          </div>
          <span class="text-xl font-bold">Rockfall</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <span class="text-slate-600">Welcome, <%= username %> </span>
          <a
            href="/logout"
            class="rounded-lg bg-red-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-white font-medium hover:bg-red-700"
            >Logout</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 px-4">
      <aside class="hidden md:block col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Navigation</h2>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-slate-700 text-sm">
            <li><a href="#home" class="hover:text-red-600">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#prediction" class="hover:text-red-600">Rockfall Prediction</a></li>
            <li><a href="/prediction" class="hover:text-red-600">Rockfall written</a></li>
            <li><a href="#news" class="hover:text-red-600">News Section</a></li>
            <li><a href="#chat" class="hover:text-red-600">AI Chat</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-red-600">Settings</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <main class="col-span-3 space-y-6">

        <section id="home" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">Welcome to No Rockfall</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700">
            This dashboard helps you predict and monitor potential rockfall areas.
            Use the navigation to access different features like the **Rockfall Prediction**
            tool, the **News Section** for the latest updates, and the **AI Chat**
            for assistance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section id="prediction" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">Rockfall Prediction</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            Upload images of a mountainous area to have our machine learning model
            analyze it for potential rockfall risks. The predicted risk level will
            be displayed below.
          </p>

          <div class="border-2 border-dashed border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <input
              type="file"
              id="image-upload"
              accept="image/*"
              class="hidden"
            />
            <label
              for="image-upload"
              class="cursor-pointer text-red-600 font-medium hover:text-red-700"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="mx-auto h-12 w-12 text-slate-400"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M7 16a4 4 0 01-.883 2.117A4 4 0 013 20c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3s1.343-3 3-3a4 4 0 011.883-.883A4.001 4.001 0 017 16zM15 12h-4v4l-4-4 4-4v4h4zM19 12a4 4 0 01-3 1.342V15a4 4 0 00-3-1.342V12h-2v4h2v-2a4 4 0 013-1.342V12h4a4 4 0 00-4-4V5a4 4 0 014 4v3h2a4 4 0 01-4 4z"
                />
              </svg>
              <span>Click to upload image</span>
            </label>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">PNG, JPG, GIF up to 10MB</p>
          </div>

          <div id="predicted-area" class="mt-6 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 hidden">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-slate-800">Predicted Result:</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-red-600 font-bold text-xl">High Risk</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Based on image analysis</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <section id="news" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">Latest Rockfall News</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-slate-800">Rockfall closes mountain pass in Colorado</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">October 26, 2025</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">
                A significant rockfall event has led to the temporary closure of Highway 50 near Monarch Pass.
                Emergency crews are on site to clear the debris and assess the stability of the slope.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-slate-800">New drone technology for rockfall monitoring</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">October 24, 2025</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">
                Researchers at a local university have developed an AI-powered drone system to monitor
                and detect subtle movements in cliffs, potentially preventing future rockfall incidents.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="chat" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">Chat with No Rockfall AI</h2>
          <div class="h-64 overflow-y-auto border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-4 space-y-4 mb-4">
            <div class="flex justify-start">
              <div class="bg-slate-200 rounded-lg p-3 max-w-sm">
                <p class="text-sm">Hello! I'm here to help you. Ask me anything about rockfall prevention or safety.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-end">
              <div class="bg-red-600 text-white rounded-lg p-3 max-w-sm">
                <p class="text-sm">What are some common causes of rockfall?</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <form onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Message Sent!');">
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <input
                type="text"
                placeholder="Type your message..."
                class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 p-3 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-400"
              />
              <button
                type="submit"
                class="bg-red-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 font-medium"
              >
                Send
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>